title: iGO8 - ONLY for NOVOGO Navigators
description:
iGO8 - Version 2008 with Western Europe 2008


How to install:

1. UnRAR the file named "iGO8 - Version 2008 with Western Europe 2008.rar"
2. Format a 1GB SD-Card or larger
3. Copy all files you extracted to the SD-Card (folder named "iGO8" and "Novogo")
4. Plug & Play - Your Novogo GPS should work now
5. Dont worry, be happy now ;)

REMEMBER: This Software is particularly and ONLY modded for Novogo GPS system, so
	  it will ONLY work with a NOVOGO Navigator.

PS. If you only have a 1GB SD-Card, delete content
    you don't need from "x:iGO8content".

    I recommend you to delete content from folders
    named "building", "dem" and "map".

And one more thing, the first time you turn ON your device, there will take around
1,5 minute, so please be patient ;)
